title: BlazBlue Centralfiction-CODEX
description:
Combining 2D fighting game and visual novel,  the  BlazBlue  series
      has  been  supported  by  many  fighting  game  fans.   The 
      installation, BlazBlue: Centralfiction, serves as the ending to the
      Azure Saga and reveals the truth that  has ever  been  in  mystery.
      First time in this series, Naoto = Kurogane Hibiki = Kohaku  Nine =
      the = Phantom and Izanami appear as playable characters  and  three
      DLC characters from the console  version --Es  from  XBlaze  series
      that shares the same worldview as Blazblue, Mai  Natsume  from  the
      BlazeBlue spinoff manga, Remix Heart, and Susano'o, the  true  form
      of Yuki Terumi-- newly join to  bring to  a total  of  35  playable
      characters!

      For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/586140/
